              "description": {
                "paragraph": [
                  "Spilled your drink? Quick! The Quicker Picker Upper. Be ready to tackle messes and spills with Bounty Paper Towels! Each sheet is 2x more absorbent, so you can use less and pick up spills and messes quicker than the leading ordinary brand. That\u2019s why Bounty is the Quicker Picker Upper!"
